WEBVTT

00:00.898 --> 00:03.397
- Previously on The Resident...
- Hey, it's a long story,

00:03.398 --> 00:05.549
but everything's gonna be just fine.

00:05.550 --> 00:07.430
This is not on you or her.

00:07.431 --> 00:08.598
I knew she was exhausted...

00:08.599 --> 00:10.190
Focus on what you can do now.

00:10.191 --> 00:12.088
Would it be moving too fast

00:12.089 --> 00:14.280
if I invited you to Thanksgiving?

00:14.281 --> 00:16.376
I spend Thanksgiving with my family.

00:16.378 --> 00:18.324
Maybe there's something we can work out.

00:18.325 --> 00:20.251
Jessie's gone, and
she is not coming back.

00:20.252 --> 00:21.327
You're all I got, kid.

00:21.328 --> 00:23.238
We're Team Nevin, now.

00:23.239 --> 00:24.921
On a first-name basis with Dr. Cain?

00:24.922 --> 00:26.864
We go way back... he's the
one who got me this job.

00:26.865 --> 00:28.214
You have no background in health care?

00:28.215 --> 00:29.238
I have a background...

00:29.239 --> 00:30.972
in profits.

00:35.265 --> 00:37.246
If I were back home in
Queens, I would be playing

00:37.247 --> 00:38.514
flag football right now.

00:38.515 --> 00:39.907
But you're not living your Thanksgiving

00:39.908 --> 00:41.848
- traditions because...
- Intern year.

00:41.849 --> 00:43.866
The only major holiday I've
gotten off is Presidents' Day.

00:43.867 --> 00:45.480
- Mm.
- How about you?

00:45.481 --> 00:47.274
You here for Jessica?

00:47.275 --> 00:48.516
Yeah.

00:48.517 --> 00:50.349
She sent her family
back home to Tennessee

00:50.350 --> 00:51.928
to care for her Great-Grandma Addie.

00:51.929 --> 00:53.878
Man versus turkey fryer...

00:53.879 --> 00:56.566
40-year-old male with full
thickness burns on his left leg.

00:56.567 --> 00:57.925
Okay, Bay Three.

00:57.926 --> 01:00.348
Ow, my leg! God, it hurts.

01:00.349 --> 01:02.363
I swear I just thought
using a turkey fryer

01:02.364 --> 01:03.665
would cook a frozen bird faster.

01:03.666 --> 01:06.585
Fryers make frozen turkeys explode.

01:06.586 --> 01:09.613
Over and under on turkey-related
injuries today is at a 12.

01:09.614 --> 01:13.300
You're on... 50 on the over.

01:13.301 --> 01:14.709
You'll see, Pravesh.

01:14.710 --> 01:18.104
Thanksgiving is the most
dangerous holiday of the year.

01:22.569 --> 01:25.069
And retractor.

01:27.148 --> 01:30.074
After we're done, there's
an orphan potluck here.

01:30.075 --> 01:32.343
I went last year... we
all said our gratitudes

01:32.344 --> 01:33.511
and everything.

01:33.512 --> 01:35.202
Family Thanksgivings are hell.

01:35.203 --> 01:37.157
Orphan Thanksgivings are worse.

01:37.158 --> 01:39.083
But what-what's worse than hell?

01:39.084 --> 01:41.995
Small talk with strangers. Dry stuffing.

01:41.996 --> 01:45.439
Drunk Aunt Sally getting
handsy under the table.

01:46.684 --> 01:48.759
Not my aunt.

01:48.760 --> 01:50.837
For me,

01:50.838 --> 01:53.149
being in the OR is the perfect holiday.

01:53.150 --> 01:54.250
No interruptions.

01:54.251 --> 01:55.772
No CEO duties.

01:55.773 --> 01:57.981
No rushing to get to meetings.

01:57.982 --> 02:00.013
To celebrate the holiday
for giving thanks,

02:00.014 --> 02:03.683
I'd be so grateful
if you'd let me close.

02:06.704 --> 02:09.295
Thank you.

